    h3 Privacy Policy and Usage Terms
    
    p These are the terms and conditions for the usage of app, and the coverage of the privacy policy. 

    h4 Terms and Conditions

    p We provide easy and secure access to our app but we will not be responsible for any time of information that will be shared using our questionnaire form, over the internet. 

